com.hp.jipp.encoding

Class MutableAttributeGroup

  • com.hp.jipp.encoding.MutableAttributeGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeGroup, PrettyPrintable

    public class MutableAttributeGroup
implements AttributeGroup

    An interface AttributeGroup which may be altered. Insertion order is preserved.

    Note:

    • the addition of any interface Attribute replaces any existing one with the same interface AttributeType.

    • use drop or minusAssign, not remove.

    See Also:
    interface AttributeGroup, interface Attribute, interface AttributeType, drop, minusAssign, remove
